node.text:
Past 1.5 years have been very difficult and challenging. In this crazy time everyone is working and giving their best. 

Not just health workers but also our Mothers. Taking care of both work and home, or just managing everything when all the family members are at home.

So, this Mother’s Day gift your mother a well thought out gift – Aesthetic Mother’s Journal ❤

This journal with help them gets started with their journey of journaling. To make this process easy and interesting I have accumulated of variety of open-ended questions and prompts. Not only this I have also included a lot of inspirational quotes. 

BONUS: Psychology based mindfulness worksheets🧘🏻‍♀️😌

What are you waiting for!!!!💣

🔴Order Now through Amazon
  Or
🔴Click on the link in the bio

Disclaimer: The product might not be available to the in specific areas of some countries. DM or any inquiry

#canada #bc #vancouver #journaling #mothersday #mothersdaygift #canadabc

“If there is something that means something to you, you should not postpone it for a single day.” 
- Sadhguru 🌼

So here I am following what I feel like I always wanted to do - explore the world. British Columbia is just one step, there is a long way to go😌🔥.

I also want to encourage you guys to do something that you really want to do. 😌

🍁
🍁
🍁
